oc:kn_286345ae a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Procedure ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When building a complete data pipeline" ;
    oc:directiveContent "1. Define data sources and extraction filters. 2. Design merge/join logic for multi-source pipelines. 3. Write transformation functions (clean, map, aggregate). 4. Configure data destinations with write mode. 5. Set schedule with cron pattern. 6. Add data quality checks (schema, stats, business rules). 7. Configure monitoring alerts." ;
    oc:stepOrder 1 .

oc:kn_28d04082 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When loading data to destinations" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never skip data quality checks (schema validation, null rates, duplicate detection) even for small or trusted data sources." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Data quality issues propagate downstream and compound; catching them at load time prevents corrupt analytics." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_577b395b a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When orchestrating multiple pipelines" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Pipeline dependencies must be explicitly declared — downstream pipelines cannot start until all upstream extracts complete." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Implicit dependencies cause race conditions and partial data loads that are difficult to diagnose." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_68629b9f a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:OutputFormat ;
    oc:directiveContent """# {Pipeline Name}
## Pipeline Overview
{Source1} + {Source2} → Transform → {Dest1} + {Dest2}
## Schedule
- Runs: {cron_schedule}
- Timezone: {tz}
- Retry: {n} attempts
## Extract
### {Source Name}
```yaml
source: {source}
filter: {filter}
fields: [{fields}]
```
## Transform
```javascript
